trends: There has been one other sighting in Florence Township
There were no other sightings in Florence Township on or around April 5th 2002
divs: Sighting Details We were driving west along a town road and abright light much like that of a plane was traveling in front of us(were in thecar. It dipped lower then arced upward and was gone aproxx. 3-4 seconds. Indisbelief I continued to look for it but there was nothing in sight.
Summary: small bright light 1000ft dipping low, arc up, gon
